OL,3,CHuw Edwards stripped of Eisteddfod
OL,4,Chonour after indecent images plea
OL,6,FHuw Edwards has been expelled from the
OL,7,FGorsedd, one of the highest honours in
OL,8,FWelsh public life.
OL,10,FThe news comes eight days after the
OL,11,Fformer BBC newsreader pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fto making indecent images of children,
OL,13,Fwith seven of the 41 images being of
OL,14,Fthe most serious type.
OL,16,FHis membership of the Eisteddfod has
OL,17,Fbeen terminated and he has also been
OL,18,Fexpelled from Gorsedd Cymru, one of
OL,19,Fthe highest accolades in Welsh public
OL,20,Flife.
