OL,6,FThe induction into the Gorsedd
OL,7,Frecognises individuals for their
OL,8,Fachievements and their commitment to
OL,9,Fthe Welsh language, Wales and its
OL,10,Flocal communities. They are usually
OL,11,Fgiven to those who have succeeded in
OL,12,Fthe fields of law, science, sports,
OL,13,Fjournalism, media, local or national
OL,14,Factivities or the arts.
