OL,6,FA statement from the National
OL,7,FEisteddfod issued on Thursday, 8
OL,8,FAugust said: "Following a unanimous
OL,9,Fvote at today's Eisteddfod Court
OL,10,Fmeeting, the board of trustees has
OL,11,Fdecided to activate Section 4 (a) (iv)
OL,12,Fof the its constitution to terminate
OL,13,FHuw Edwards' membership of the
OL,14,FEisteddfod and as a result, he will
OL,15,Falso be expelled from Gorsedd Cymru."
