OL,6,FThe Eisteddfod is one of a number of
OL,7,Finstitutions and organisations Edwards
OL,8,Fwas previously affiliated to in Wales
OL,9,Fwhich have been taking actions to
OL,10,Fdisassociate themselves from him since
OL,11,Fhis court appearance.
OL,13,FEdwards had already lost his position
OL,14,Fas vice-president of the National
OL,15,FChurches Trust, and Cardiff and Bangor
OL,16,FUniversities have said they are
OL,17,Freviewing honours granted to him in
OL,18,Fthe past.
