OL,6,FElsewhere, plaques were removed from
OL,7,FCardiff Castle and a mural was painted
OL,8,Fover in his hometown of Llangennech,
OL,9,FCarmarthenshire.
OL,11,FEdwards pleaded guilty to making
OL,12,Findecent images of children, shortly
OL,13,Fafter the Metropolitan Police revealed
OL,14,Fhe had been arrested in November 2023
OL,15,Fand charged in June this year,
OL,16,Ffollowing an investigation separate to
OL,17,Flast year's scandal.
