OL,6,FEdwards resigned from the BBC in April
OL,7,F"on the basis of medical advice from
OL,8,Fhis doctors" after unrelated
OL,9,Fallegations that he paid a young
OL,10,Fperson for sexually explicit photos.
OL,12,FPolice found no evidence of criminal
OL,13,Fbehaviour in the matter.
OL,15,FEdwards will next appear in court on
OL,16,FSeptember 16.
