OL,6,FBBC director general Tim Davie has
OL,7,Fdefended his decision to employ
OL,8,FEdwards until April, five months after
OL,9,Fhe was told of Edwards' arrest in
OL,10,FNovember 2023 over the most serious
OL,11,Fcategory of indecent images of
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,FIt comes amid reports that the BBC is
OL,15,Fset to retain the Bafta it won for
OL,16,Froyal coverage fronted by Edwards,
OL,17,Fwhile individual gongs awarded to the
OL,18,Fdisgraced newsreader remain under
OL,19,Freview.
