OL,6,FThe Academy is reviewing seven
OL,7,Findividual presenter prizes handed to
OL,8,FEdwards by the Bafta Cymru Awards
OL,9,Fbetween 2002 to 2017.
OL,11,FA Bafta spokesperson said: "Like
OL,12,Feveryone in the industry and country
OL,13,Fwe were shocked by the news ` given
OL,14,Fthe seriousness of this abhorrent
OL,15,Fcrime, we are reviewing."
OL,17,FThe Bafta won by the BBC in 2012, for
OL,18,FEdwards' coverage of Prince William
OL,19,Fand Kate Middleton's wedding in 2011,
OL,20,Fwill remain.
